IMAPAccount qq
Host imap.qq.com
User 517926804@qq.com
PassCmd "pass show mail/517926804@qq.com"
Port 993
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
# CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
CertificateFile /opt/homebrew/etc/ca-certificates/cert.pem  # MacOS

##
# Remote
IMAPStore qq-remote
Account qq

# Local
MaildirStore qq-local
Path ~/.mail/qq.com/
Inbox ~/.mail/qq.com/Inbox

# Channels
Channel qq-inbox
Far :qq-remote:"INBOX"
Near :qq-local:"Inbox"
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel qq-drafts
Far :qq-remote:"Drafts"
Near :qq-local:"Drafts"
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel qq-sent
Far :qq-remote:"Sent Messages"
Near :qq-local:"Sent"
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel qq-trash
Far :qq-remote:"Deleted Messages"
Near :qq-local:"Trash"
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *

## Groups
Group qq
Channel qq-inbox
Channel qq-drafts
Channel qq-sent
Channel qq-trash
